{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f85fd6b74d","title":"甘肃民勤县孙润华同志关于停止收购代食品及某些付食品的建议","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8ac3e492ad","index":0,"year":1960,"month":12,"day":12,"articleId":"f85fd6b74d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2463ba7488","type":"title","text":"甘肃民勤县孙润华同志关于停止收购代食品及某些付食品的建议","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f85fd6b74d"},{"id":"b00a9a890c","type":"subtitle","text":"（姚怀顺同志1960年12月12日19时半电话）","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f85fd6b74d"},{"id":"1808243f45","type":"appellation","text":"省委生活安排小组综合办公室：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f85fd6b74d"},{"id":"656c737319","type":"paragraph","text":"民勤的物资收购问题，需要给予及时的解决，不然，收购人员继续收购，收不到就强迫、违法乱纪又会产生，弄的很紧张，例如：有的群众把糖萝卜、黄蒿籽藏起来，实际还是收不到，即使能收起，也没有多少，反而影响人民生活需要，这对当前安排人民生活很不利。因此，我建议：在民勤，除棉花留足人民迫切需要的以外，其他凡能吃的东西或群众当前需要的东西，都应停止收购。这不单是民勤的问题，在灾情严重的县，都应该这样，是否妥当，请作参考。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f85fd6b74d"},{"id":"67c57ce3cb","type":"paragraph","text":" 孙润华1930年12月12日19时半","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f85fd6b74d"},{"id":"b14b6aed7a","type":"paragraph","text":"（请王国瑞同志提出意见）","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f85fd6b74d"}],"page":{"id":"b423ecf8a6","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"f85fd6b74d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}